/Cat_Stevens\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"@yusufdikec)August\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 976}, {\"ngram\": \"This exchange\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"over 8.5 million views\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"less than 12 hours\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the 51-year-old's casual attire as he fired with his other hand in pocket at the Chateauroux Shooting Centre that made him a global sensation.\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 51-year-old's casual attire\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"his other hand\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"pocket\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1180}, {\"ngram\": \"the Chateauroux Shooting Centre\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While most pistol shooters wear visors, chunky ear-defenders and shooting lenses with a blinder to shut out distractions and enhance focus, Dikec had only an yellow ear plug in as he hit the range.\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most pistol shooters\", \"from\": 1257, \"to\": 1277}, {\"ngram\": \"visors\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"ear-defenders\", \"from\": 1298, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"lenses\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1331}, {\"ngram\": \"a blinder\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"distractions\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"focus\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"Dikec\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"only an yellow ear\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1419}, {\"ngram\": \"the range\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His silver hair, intense gaze, normal glasses and a jersey that looked like a regular t-shirt intrigued netizens.\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1557, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.